        <div class="header">
            <h2>About</h2>
            <p id="Basics">Greetings! My name is Dódi.<br><br>I am a <a href="https://www.ed.ac.uk/profile/jozsef-wells" target="_blank">linguistics PhD candidate</a> in the <a href="https://www.ed.ac.uk/ppls/linguistics-and-english-language" target="_blank">School of Philosophy, Psychology and Language Science</a> at <a href="https://www.ed.ac.uk/" target="_blank">the University of Edinburgh</a>.</p>

            <br><p>My PhD research is on <i>Language Policy and Planning (LPP)</i> in Taiwan, specifically I am interested in the <i>Language Vitality</i> of <u>Taiwanese local</u> and <u>indigenous languages</u>.</p>
            
            <br><p class="location">From June 2023 to August 2023, I will be at the <a href="https://www1.ihp.sinica.edu.tw/en/People/Visiting" target="_blank">Institute of History and Philology, Academia Sinica</a> finishing my PhD as a junior visiting scholar.</p>
            <p class="location"><i>I am based out of Edinburgh, Scotland, & Urbana, Illinois, USA.</i></p>
            

        </div>
       
